data.description: Closing costs available on reasonable priced offer or ask about 2/1 interest rate buydown! Assumable VA Loan at 4.75%. Large, updated and charming 2 story home in West Hampton! Situated on a rare extended lot, this home features a large, fully fenced backyard perfect for relaxing or entertaining. An inviting front porch welcomes you into the spacious first floor featuring 2 living rooms, dining room, kitchen outfitted with plenty of cabinets and countertop space, and a downstairs bedroom and full bath. 3 bedrooms upstairs plus an additional flex room/office and full bath. Minutes to downtown Hampton and easily commutable to Newport News Shipyard, Langley, Eustis and Naval Station Norfolk. Enjoy the short distance to explore the Hampton Marina and close to entertainment, restaurants, shopping, museums, Hampton University and the Hampton Medical Center. 3% closing costs on reasonable offer or ask about 2/1 rate buydown!
